query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `availability_requests` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `interpreter_id` int NOT NULL,
  `client_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `client_email` varchar(320) NOT NULL,
  `client_phone` varchar(50),
  `requested_date` timestamp NOT NULL,
  `requested_time` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `duration` int NOT NULL,
  `location` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `source_language` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `target_language` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `notes` text,
  `status` enum('pending', 'confirmed', 'declined', 'cancelled') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `interpreter_notes` text,
  `confirmation_token` varchar(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `interpreter_id_idx` (`interpreter_id`),
  INDEX `status_idx` (`status`),
  INDEX `requested_date_idx` (`requested_date`),
  INDEX `confirmation_token_idx` (`confirmation_token`)
);
